# E-Commerce Backend

## Features

- User CRUD Operations
- Product CRUD Operations
- Order Creation
- MongoDB Database
- Express.js Backend

## Folder Structure

models/
services/
handlers/
routes/

## API Endpoints

### Users

POST /users
GET /users
PUT /users/:id
DELETE /users/:id

### Products

POST /products
GET /products
PUT /products/:id
DELETE /products/:id

### Orders

POST /orders
GET /orders

## Technologies Used

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- Mongoose
